{"tid":569105,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【引以為鑑】掛住睇手機！後生仔雪地跣低 頭撼石壆亡","createTime":"2018-02-22T11:26:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-22T11:26:33.000Z","uid":84436,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"534b5d249ef118bfe7d9d6759c50424c9e453791","tid":569105,"uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T11:26:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180222/57860612\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180222%2F57860612&d=jy%2FSht6CnzJSEoys9N7VJ8KJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=3114cad4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180222%2F57860612&h=ad396ceb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180222/57860612</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n走路要專心，不要只顧看手機，否則分分鐘連命都不保！前日，甘肅張掖一名年輕男子，便在濕滑的雪地上，邊走邊低頭看手機，結果腳下一滑，腦後撞上路邊石壆。救護人員接報到場後，為男子進行急救，惜已回天乏術。<br />\n<br />\n據目擊者稱，當時有一家三口在路上走着，估計他們是去拜年。「然後那個小伙子就摔倒了，是看手機，然後摔倒，頭（後腦勺）就一下着在那個道路牙子上。」"}]}